         <para number='1' comment='Eat Cigar commentary'>
         You touch the self ignition tab on your cigar and place it to your lips, inhaling the smoke as you do. Clearly you have not heeded the Surgeon Generals warning about the negative health effects of smoking. You start to feel queezy, the room starts to spin, all noise around you seems amplified and the lights much brighter. You start to sweat and you feel your heart pumping hard as you slowly slip from consciousness........
         </para>

         <para number='2' comment='Eat Cigar commentary'>
         You awake to find yourself in the Infirmary, that was quite a turn you had, you pick yourself up and feel a little queasy. It seems that cigar was just no good for you at all, in fact, it managed to wipe 20 points off of your stamina!! Who said the Surgeon General was making it up when he claimed that smoking was bad for your health!!
         </para>

         <para number='4' comment='response to wisp'>
         Who told you about Wisp? What do you want to know? Well, all I will tell you is that Wisp used to be the centre of my families operations back in the time when it was the priciple planet in the Cloud system. It was abandoned many years ago, became uninhabitable you know. Anything else you hear about my family and Wisp is pure conjecture, fantasy, no substance in it at all.
         </para>

         <para number='5' comment='response to Cumulus'>
         Cumulus, huh. I don't like it there, too much pomp and ceremony. And its where that pompous Cloudbase lives. The self styled leader of the Cloudarians, I don't think so!! Us Flumps have more right to the throne, but somehow, he managed to get his hands on it. I tell you, that planet just is'nt big enough for his ego, but one day ......................
         </para>

         <para number='6' comment='response to Cloudbase'>
         That arrogant ego maniac, have no time for him ......... oh, you mean the space station we are on right now. A fine piece of engineering, did you know my family helped to finance it!!! Its our base of operations now, you will always find me here in the bar, just pop in and I can sort you with anything you might need.
         </para>

         <para number='7' comment='rsponse to Nimbus'>
         I like it on Nimbus, its not everyones cup of tea though. Its the biological planet here in the Cloud system. You need to be an earthy type to live down there. So if you are a little feeble or weak, they will take advantage of you, but hey, just mention my name and they will be as nice as apple pie!!
         </para>

         <para number='8' comment='response to cloudarian'>
         The Cloudarians go back to the dawn of civilisation you know. The premier race in the universe, not that you would think so by looking at that waste of space Cloudbase. Us Flumps are what epitomises the greatness of the race, intellectual, strong, resourceful and dammed attractive too, but you could see that the moment you layed eyes on me.
         </para>

         <para number='9' comment='response to cloud'>
         Huh, this used to be such a clear area of space, its just a coincidence that the Cloud system is shrouded in Cloud. But that suits my operation down to the ground. Its cloudy because of the over industrialisation on Wisp, it was abandoned many centuries ago because it became uninhabitable. The pollution from there has leaked out into space and thats why it is so Cloudy.
         </para>

